data.description: Welcome to your dream home-an updated 5-bedroom house with a spacious basement! This stunning property offers the perfect blend of modern amenities and classic charm, providing you with the ultimate living experience. Step inside to discover a beautifully updated interior with tasteful finishes and a neutral color palette that complements any style. The floor plan ensures seamless flow between rooms, perfect for both daily living and entertaining. The basement of this home offers endless possibilities. With its generous square footage, it can be transformed into a home theater, a game room, a fitness area, or any other space that suits your needs. Conveniently located near community pool, walking trails & pond.
